# Stryker mutation-testing sandbox: transient per-package copies of src/ created
# under packages/*/.stryker-tmp/ during the tier-4 mutation checks. Byte-identical
# to the real source, so leaving it un-ignored makes the jscpd duplication analyzer
# (gitignore-aware) count every sandbox file as a clone of its original.
.stryker-tmp/
*.cover
*.py,cover
.hypothesis/
.pytest_cache/
cover/

